[30;1m592 | [0m[35m        self.device = None  # detected only once in the first forward[0m
[30;1m593 | [0m[35m        # empty cache before and after lm_head at first token (by default on arc)[0m

[30;1m597 | [0m[35m        # since performance isn't impacted.[0m
